### Get all feedback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get feedback statistics for a period (last 30 days)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/statistics?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get feedback statistics for a specific menu item
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/statistics?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z&menuItemId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get feedback statistics by menu item
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/statistics/by-item?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get filtered feedback - by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/filtered?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get filtered feedback - by rating (positive feedback only, 4+ stars)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/filtered?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z&minRating=4
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get filtered feedback - by rating (negative feedback only, 2 or less stars)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/filtered?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z&maxRating=2
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get filtered feedback - by menu item name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/filtered?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z&menuItemName=Burger
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Get filtered feedback - combined filters (positive feedback for specific item)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/filtered?start=2025-09-21T00:00:00Z&end=2025-10-21T23:59:59Z&minRating=4&menuItemName=Burger
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}

### Set feedback sentiment (batch update)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/feedback/sentiment
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "sentiment": 1,
    "category": "positive"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "sentiment": -1,
    "category": "negative"
  }
]
